{
  "texts": [
    "To prepare for the interviews, we sent the questions to the coaches in advance.",
    "Each interview lasted roughly an hour, and each coach received a compensation of $80 for their participation.",
    "The following subsections provide an aggregated summary of the interview responses.",
    "While our dataset entails the complete answers to a total of six questions, this paper specifically highlights the four questions that directly influenced the design of the dataset (see Table 2).",
    "These four questions primarily focus on the types of data and annotations that should be included for the analysis of badminton stroke actions."
  ]
}